item.title: How do i change spawn of players?
item.dc:creator: @kilermage3 kilermage3
item.description:
@kilermage3 wrote:

Um, get the coords of where you start at then go to player.java and search for the x coords that you got earlier and then just hit crtl + f and enter the x coords like “3254” or whatever the coords where and then just click find and then change the coords to the new coords you want the players to start, then close and save, then compile and your done.
